	pf_h323_no_answer_timeout.patch
	$Revision$
	$Date$
	Behavioral change.

	This patch makes Asterisk disable the timeout OpenH323 automatically
	uses by default when an outgoing call is placed to abort it if nobody
	answer after 1 minute.

Index: asterisk-1.2.27/channels/h323/ast_h323.cpp
===================================================================
